mental health outcomes? Most theoretical literature from a develop-
mental perspective (e.g. Beauchaine & Gatzke-Kopp, 2013; Hinshaw,
2013; Kerig, Ludlow, & Wenar, 2012; Mash & Dozios, 2003 ) suggests
that negative early experiences result in an increased risk of psycholog-
ical distress and symptoms of psychopathology; however, what are
the mechanisms that convert adverse environments into mental
health difﬁculties?
